item.title: The Ripple Effect: Minnesota Twins Launch New City Connect Uniform
item.description: The Minnesota Twins dropped their new 10,000 Lakes themed City Connect uniform. We spoke with the team and explored every aspect of the new uniform together.

item.title: Minnesota Golden Gophers Unveil New Football Uniforms
item.description: Minnesota unveiled three new uniforms on Friday morning, marking the first significant overhaul to the Golden Gophers’ look since the 2018 season.
